      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-900 relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Für dich</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm mt-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <span>Selbstständig, Freelancer oder Unternehmer</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <span>Du willst <strong>selbst alles können</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <span>4-6 Stunden/Woche Zeit</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <span>Echte Skills, nicht nur Theorie</span>
